-7a7e-475e-8bab-edd352210569-resize-950x633.jpg\" height=\"633\" width=\"949\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" itemprop=\"contentUrl url\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/phoenix-picture\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"author\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePatrick Harboun\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe father-son duo\u0026#39;s original entry was built during the height of the pandemic lockdown, a time when many turned to creative outlets for solace. Sharing their mutual love for Daft Punk\u0026#39;s timeless music, they crafted a stunning replica of the duo\u0026#39;s iconic pyramid stage from their \u0026#34;Alive 2007\u0026#34; tour.\u003c/p\u003e\u003csection id=\"phx-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eScroll to Continue\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"phx-4\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch2 role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003eRecommended Articles\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003cp\u003eDespite winning first place, the stunning set never saw commercial production. However, the Harbouns are going for greatness one more time after becoming re-inspired by \u003ca href=\"https://edm.com/lifestyle/daft-punk-appearing-pharrell-lego-biopic-piece-by-piece\"\u003eDaft Punk\u0026#39;s cameo\u003c/a\u003e in Pharrell\u0026#39;s upcoming LEGO animation film \u003cem\u003ePiece By Piece\u003c/em\u003e, Patrick tells \u003cem\u003eEDM.com\u003c/em\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"\u003e\u003cphoenix-picture\u003e\u003ca\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://edm.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjA5ODYzNzIxNTc5NzE4MDk3/8911f662-26f1-4b73-8df5-3a882094cecc-resize-1200x675.webp 380w, https://edm.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjA5ODYzNzIxNTc5NzE4MDk3/8911f662-26f1-4b73-8df5-3a882094cecc-resize-1200x675.webp 620w, https://edm.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjA5ODYzNzIxNTc5NzE4MDk3/8911f662-26f1-4b73-8df5-3a882094cecc-resize-1200x675.webp 700w\"/\u003e\u003csource sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://edm.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjA5ODYzNzIxNTc5NzE4MDk3/8911f662-26f1-4b73-8df5-3a882094cecc-resize-1200x675.jpg 380w, https://edm.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjA5ODYzNzIxNTc5NzE4MDk3/8911f662-26f1-4b73-8df5-3a882094cecc-resize-1200x675.jpg 620w, https://edm.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjA5ODYzNzIxNTc5NzE4MDk3/8911f662-26f1-4b73-8df5-3a882094cecc-resize-1200x675.jpg 700w\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"8911f662-26f1-4b73-8df5-3a882094cecc-resize-1200x675\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://edm.com/.image/t_share/MjA5ODYzNzIxNTc5NzE4MDk3/8911f662-26f1-4b73-8df5-3a882094cecc-resize-1200x675.webp\" data-src=\"https://edm.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjA5ODYzNzIxNTc5NzE4MDk3/8911f662-26f1-4b73-8df5-3a882094cecc-resize-1200x675.jpg\" height=\"675\" width=\"1012\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" itemprop=\"contentUrl url\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/phoenix-picture\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"author\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePatrick Harboun\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eTheir new design is live on the LEGO Ideas platform, where projects can garner fan votes for a chance to become official sets. If successful by voter demand, it will celebrate Daft Punk\u0026#39;s enduring legacy in both music and pop culture.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c